and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxonaA='a","text_ar":"سَخْنَا=ءَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxuwnapF","text_ar":"سُخُونَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isoxinapF","text_ar":"اـِسْخِنَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in the JK erroneously written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^soxinapF","text_ar":"اسْخِنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":") contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboridapF","text_ar":"اـِبْرِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily I find,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experience, in myself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excess of heat arising from pain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fever."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonapu AlEayoni","text_ar":"سُخْنَةُ العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qur~atuhaA","text_ar":"قُرَّتُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an inflamed, state of the eye, by reason of weeping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sorrow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heat in the tears of the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 1, last sentence]. (S, L, K.)"}],"source_refs":["L","K","JK","S"]},{"entry_id":"n19249","headword_ar":"سِخْنَةٌ","root":"sxn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph. ―         -b2-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka biAlA^amori Einoda sixonatihi","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ بِالاَمْرِ عِنْدَ سِخْنَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep thou to the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"while it is in its first state, before it become cold"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. unmanageable, like cold iron]. (L.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19250","headword_ar":"سَخَنَةٌ","root":"sxn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxonapN","text_ar":"سُخْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}